Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这题考前猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这题也是轻轻松松解决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯  最近很用功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样高中入学考试也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第57话\N一切源自桃源乡之夜  前篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又要回国啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事用不着这么大声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊  知道现在是什么时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道归知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有很重要的模试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸是?那什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模拟试验  就是考试的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是什么“烤事”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  只要三天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想预习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得戈薇姑娘也蛮辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直留在这里就轻松多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就那么喜欢那个\N叫“烤事”的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想回去故乡个三天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故乡?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要回驱魔师的村子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想修理飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为使用过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有三天喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  那我也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天后我会到枫姥姥的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算难得能好好休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚在就不能好好休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉会答应的这么干脆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是跑到这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得收你当弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然逃避修行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讨厌风吹日晒\N与饿的前胸贴后背
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不想最后被逼着上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像蝼蚁一般死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这些话的不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶…饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经对世间没有留恋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才让你进入桃源乡\N修炼成为仙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不想当仙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么可怕的地方我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  好浓的雾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得这果实好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…人面果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面果?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以人类作为养分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结出很像人脸的果实的妖树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖树…就是妖怪树吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是会有这么多漂过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表示是相当大的树呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种时代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来场大型战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥料就多的用不完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种深山里会有战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  去调查看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正一定会在意的念不下书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且考试是三天后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没闲功夫休息啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要无视我自己走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是赶时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点解决掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面果树就在这上面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这峭壁的上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么巨大的人面果树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是头一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这股不祥的妖气…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是用了很多人当养分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气砍断那棵妖树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们也帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到把你们一个个送到峭壁上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳都下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉一定打算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在太阳下山前解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是朔日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朔日…新月!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的妖力会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成普通人类的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以犬夜叉才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有长生不老的果实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是这种东西连我都吃腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,养着这棵妖树吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有感受到妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却散发出浓厚的死人臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呸  找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懒得跟你废话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要砍掉这棵怪异的树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你胆敢阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻碍你又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连你一起砍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付这肥嘟嘟的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙起不了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是打哪来的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你以为赢得了仙人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我是桃源乡的仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃果人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葫芦变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是  是你变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  这不是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真的是仙人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的事别让我说太多遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是仙人  为什么要这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  想要进来这里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只妖怪一定是上好的肥料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只差一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  真让人刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你的力气这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到今天是朔日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳下山以后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉就会变成普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子好像有人住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们住在这个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箱庭也变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是我们正在缩小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才在走路的小小男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是箱庭的内部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啦\N我们也得住在这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想个办法出去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:13:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且四魂碎片也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还搞不清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先听听看这里的人怎么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  大家在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里并非真实的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  有没有在听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别打扰我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们妨碍到修炼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修炼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这做成为仙人的修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为仙人的修炼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拥有仙人之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能从桃果人大人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到长生不老的人面果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃果人?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是把你们\N困在这的罪魁祸首吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃果人大人是将我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从饥饿与战乱之中\N救出来的大恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都只是生锈的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何那小子一挥\N就变成了大刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  管他的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙已经掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我却没有妖化成妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来妖力已经减弱成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然被困在这种鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火鼠衣被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子不能再拖下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只好从内部破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一点点伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:15:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:15:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西才不放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个死胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我出去就把你大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋!浑蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爪子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  妖力消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有两块
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意儿只要有一块
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能让我的身体把刀子弹回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是金刚不坏之身了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  愈来愈多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再拖下去会被溶化的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做那些事就能成为仙人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要拥有仙术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确需要肉体的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是精神方面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也必须更加强韧才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  那边的诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来你们不是这里的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是武士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎和其他人不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  其实没差多少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因为战败
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在逃到这个山谷的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被桃果人抓来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想成为仙人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:18:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们会一点仙术的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会变成人面果的养分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃果人与人面果在对话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面果  还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没结出长生不老的果实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再拿更多的仙人之魂来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙人这东西  哪可能有那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要照我的话做就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  人面果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很罗唆耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把这个拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就说不了话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住  住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我代你保管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把仙人之魂拿给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  战败的武士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去吧!给我好好修行!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那很可能是四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是能感受到\N四魂碎片的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那家伙根本就是坏仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来  所谓的仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说如果没有舍弃世俗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入独特的境界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法成为仙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这里的这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法成为仙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是为了成为人面果的肥料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而被强迫修行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙完全\N把我说的事情当耳边风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也一起去告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了\N就算知道这些事也逃不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有什么方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能逃得出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…你一定要平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变的会感觉到痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子已经变成普通人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么样才能离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀鞘在呼唤铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙一定在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  这样也许有用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的  这把烂刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错  就是这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死胖子  觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是刚才那个妖怪小鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是还你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子  找死!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死胖子  你是从哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼  该觉悟的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然够厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做才能逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.83,0:22:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候犬夜叉一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.10,0:22:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都找不到出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论走到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都只有墙壁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:22:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不就成为仙人之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成人面果的养分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不就这样在这里等死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这两种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.29,0:23:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何梦想或希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是梦就醒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种恶梦我不想再做了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:49.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:24:01.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:08.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:17.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:24.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:31.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.15,0:24:38.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.62,0:24:46.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:54.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.14,0:25:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是梦  一定是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.11,0:25:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  捏我一下看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.31,0:25:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…果然不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.18,0:25:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你现在因为朔日
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.32,0:25:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而变成了普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.92,0:25:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能打赢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.85,0:25:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个施展怪异仙术的桃果人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.62,0:25:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要为了我舍命?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.96,0:25:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  不行啊  犬夜叉!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.40,0:25:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.70,0:25:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切源自桃源乡之夜  后篇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.27,0:25:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黎明…快点来临吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.40,0:25:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
